    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blind Man's Sun</strong> is a visual novel in the genres of “psychological horror” and “mystical detective”. Together with Jack Collingwood, you'll embark on a journey to help his companion Iris recover her lost memories and uncover who condemned her to eternal torment.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plot</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes it feels like life’s finally coming together. Money problems solved, your marriage is perfect, and your little girl’s growing up happy and healthy. <br>Feels like it. <br>Then the fog clears, and you realize that &quot;happy life&quot; is just a bubble waiting to be popped by a drunk driver. <br>My wife died, and I ended up in a coma. Technically, I came out of it blind, but honestly... that’s just the start.  <br>Too long to explain here. Check out the novel—there’s Iris, my possession, and the Midnight Sun.  <br>All the crazy stuff I got dragged into.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hope you enjoy the ride. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story inspired by 2000s comic books.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two visual styles to choose from.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A charismatic protagonist who will troll you. Yes, player, I'm talking about you.</p></li></ul>",
